{
  "texts": [
    "They can be required to run their written text through automated paraphrasing tools to identify improvement areas and enhance readability before submission.",
    "They can also be shown how to use large language models as assistive and personalized learning tools that guide their construction process while remaining in control over the whole writing task.",
    "Coupled with appreciating the capabilities and positive benefits that ADWTs may bring to students' learning experiences is to be cognizant of their impact on academic integrity.",
    "We present these in the next section.",
    "The introduction and continued advancements of generative AI technologies are changing how people learn and work."
  ]
}